The big-screen superhero blockbuster, “Spider-Man: No Way Home” was voted best movie at the 2022 MTV Movie & TV Awards on Sunday night. Zendaya also dominated the MTV Movie and TV Awards on Sunday as her teen drama “Euphoria” bagged the best show category award. Stars Tom Holland and Zendaya accepted the award via separate pretaped video speeches, according to Hollywood Reporters. See full list of winners for the scripted movies categories below: BEST MOVIE
